<h3> <span class="mw-headline" id="esp8089"> esp8089 </span></h3>
<p>ESP8089 driver is available from <a class="external text" href="https://github.com/linux-rockchip/linux-rockchip">linux-rockchip repository</a> under <tt>drivers/net/esp8089</tt>. Please note that there are different versions of this driver in various branches.
</p><p><a class="external autonumber" href="https://github.com/Icenowy/esp8089">[1]</a> is a standalone driver verified to be usable on an <a href="/Aoson_M751s" title="Aoson M751s">Aoson M751s</a> device and a mainline 4.6 kernel.
</p>
