<p>The <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.rdamicro.com/products/Detail_273.aspx">RDA5990P</a> is a single chip solution which includes Wifi, Bluetooth and an FM radio. Some code for this wifi chip is available in <a class="external text" href="https://github.com/linuxium/3188-SRC-ORIG/tree/master/kernel/drivers/net/wireless/rda5990">a Rockchip RK3188 kernel tree</a>, but nobody has tested or ported this code yet.
</p>
